            <lb/>
4<lb/>
fires are active in elevating or extending<lb/>
Land - |_ So that the principle of Change<lb/>
seems essential in all terrestrial nature;<lb/>
but by the <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
