               <name xml:id="tag4" type="person">
          Platonic
        </name>
            </rs> Theory. -<lb/>
- In this theory All the<lb/>
phenomena of Geology are<lb/>
supposed the result of an<lb/>
uniform system in which there<lb/>
            <lb/>
            <pb xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
