            <add xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0">fitted</add>
            <lb/>
            <add xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0">for</add> an exertion of the <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
