                rend="underline">imagination</hi> . -<lb/>
- The Person who is attached to<lb/>
Geological enquiries, can scarcely<lb/>
ever want objects of employment<lb/>
&amp; of interest. -<lb/>
- The Ground on which he treads. -<lb/>
The Country which surrounds him;<lb/>
&amp; even the Rocks &amp; Stones removed<lb/>
from their natural positions by Art,<lb/>
are all capable of affording him<lb/>
