- - To the Geological Enquirers,<lb/>
every Mountain Chain, offers decided<lb/>
proofs of the great alterations<lb/>
that the Globe has undergone. --<lb/>
The most sublime speculations are<lb/>
awakened. - the mind is carried<lb/>
into past ages. - New forms of<lb/>
            <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">existence</hi> are presented to it,<lb/>
&amp; a boundless enquiry. - the<lb/>
